saja"? Tentu saja kau memerlukannya.

107
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:41,580
Ibu akan mencari tahu tentang
bimbingan belajar untukmu.

108
00:08:44,840 --> 00:08:46,090
Tidak apa-apa...

109
00:08:46,090 --> 00:08:47,530
Selamat datang!

110
00:08:54,300 --> 00:08:56,910
<i>[Gong Tae Kwang]</i>

111
00:09:01,070 --> 00:09:03,080
