184
00:16:22,030 --> 00:16:23,470
Lee Eun Bi.

185
00:16:24,680 --> 00:16:27,090
Kau harus mengambil tanggung
jawab atas apa yang kau katakn.

186
00:16:27,090 --> 00:16:29,360
